    "body" : "Its less an issiue of the linked code changing (we can trivally edit the link to go to a specific commit instead) but 1) a copyright problem (the linked repository doesn&#39;t have a repo license, which means we <b>must</b> assume standard all-rights-reserved) and 2) the repository, as far as SO users control it, might disappear at any time, leaving nothing usefull in this question."
